<title>Hallelujah Amen</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Jerusalem khawpi hawih chu Zion,
 Martar haw leh Angel vamte lenna;
 Mi gilote chu Krista zalin,
 Leng un au zie gam ni tum lohna achun.

[V2]
 Hallelujah Lalpa lopi Amen,
 Hallelujah Amen Hallelujah;
 Ei hukdam dingin a hung pieng ie!
 Aw ka Lal Immanuel,Halleluiah.

[V3]
 2. Kraws chung achun thisan lul a luong tai,
 Isu thisan lopi Kalvari ah;
 I hukdamna diua hung luong kha,
 A lul ie Isu thisan Hallellujah.

[V4]
 3. A hungkit ni a mipi kikhawp tieng,
 Gawtmuna I suohchak nau Jubilee;
 Chapangte kipahna Lalpa chu,
 Chungnung penah Hossana'tin a sau ui.

[V5]
 4. Jerusalem kipahna Lal Messie,
 Jerusalem kipahna Lal Messie;
 Lal mina hung a kipahpih tau,
 A lul ie Isu thisan Hallelujah.</lyrics>
</song>